This automator workflow require FFMpeg and MP3 LAME. Instructions on installations can be found here
http://phongleland.wordpress.com/2010/01/27/extracting-audio-from-youtube/

To Using This Automator Workflow

Enable Applescript in the menu bar by Double-clicking the “Script Menu.menu” file in the /System/Library/CoreServices/MenuExtras folder
Move the automator file to your ~/Library/Scirpts folder

Questions can be sent to 
phongleland@gmail.com